     <div class="row"> 
      <div class="span12"> 
       <h1 class="page-header">Academic Personnel and Programs</h1> 
      </div> 
      <div class="span12"> 
       <ul class="nav nav-tabs sub-nav tab6"> 
        <li class="active"><a class="" href="index.html">Overview</a></li> 
        <li class=""><a class="" href="staff/index.html">Staff</a></li> 
        <li class=""><a class="multiline" href="academic-personnel-policy/index.html">Academic Personnel Policy</a></li> 
        <li class=""><a class="" href="compensation/index.html">Compensation</a></li> 
        <li class=""><a class="" href="data-and-analysis/index.html">Data &amp; Analysis</a></li> 
        <li class=""><a class="multiline" href="programs-and-initiatives/index.html">Programs &amp; Initiatives</a></li> 
       </ul> 
      </div> 
     </div> 
     <!-- Example row of columns --> 
     <div class="row-fluid"> 
      <div class="span4 hero-unit"> 
       <p>We advance UCâ€™s mission through innovative academic policy and programs serving UC faculty and students.</p> 
      </div> 
      <div class="span4">
       <p>Academic Personnel and Programs manages systemwide programs and develops policy supporting faculty careers at UC, including recruitment, retention, advancement, compensation, diversity, and affirmative action. We have universitywide responsibility for education abroad and exchange relationships. We provide faculty and students with opportunities to study and work in Washington, DC and Sacramento. We help prepare high school and middle school students for university opportunities. Several of our programs offer publication, media, and digital services to the UC community as well as to California and to the world.</p>
      </div> 
      <div class="span4"> 
       <div class="row-fluid dotted-bottom"> 
        <div class="span4 dept-head"> 
